metadata.name: Creation Coffee
metadata.description:
The Creation Coffee is the first token in the collection, it symbolizes the creation of the Cafe.

We’ve come a long way from the fast-paced environment of the bull market.

Collectors are curating, artists are creating, investors are researching and “gm” is everywhere.

The collection captures the calm season of the market.  

Soon the season will end and a new excitement will begin… but for now, we relax and enjoy 8-bit animated coffees.

Crypto Coffee Cafe supports cc0.
